{"tid":2387823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"曾因採訪維權律師被驅逐 德青年David Missal 惋惜香港失自由：「為不能發聲的人發聲是我的責任」","createTime":"2021-01-30T15:30:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T03:53:26.000Z","uid":48083,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"803e9639b5b88a0caeca7378c2265c5c596e90da","tid":2387823,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T15:30:32.000Z","msg":"27歲來自德國的穆德偉（David Missal）曾經在中國和香港留學，操一口流利普通話，「2018年的香港，對一個剛從北京來的人來說，感覺是個很自由的地方，當時大家都還可以遊行、在媒體上甚麼都可以說。我回德國之後，看到香港這些自由被打壓，我覺得是一個很可惜很可怕的事情。」<br />\n<br />\n穆德偉或許只是一名過客，但對香港的形勢仍是很上心，「我覺得我應該做一些事情。特別是我作為外國人在國外，為一些不能發聲的人發聲，這個在一定程度上是我的責任吧。畢竟我不會被關押，我在個自由的地方，可以說話，所以我就應該這麼做。」<br />\n<br />\n德國聯邦議會在剛過去的周一召開聽證會，討論是否因應港區國安法而制裁中港相關官員。之所以有這個聽證會，全因為一個聯署行動，去年由穆德偉和前「鍵盤戰線」發言人鄺頌晴發起，最後獲逾五萬人參與。<br />\n<br />\n穆達偉2018年在清華大學讀碩士時，因採訪維權律師，被中國取消其學生簽證，變相驅逐出境。他同年轉到港大繼續學業，體驗過那對比之下尚算自由的小城。回德後，眼見小城的自由正急速萎縮，想起之前採訪維權律師的那份感動，自覺有必要為不能發聲的人，出一分力。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37587/%E7%A9%86%E9%81%94%E5%81%89_david_missal-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-37587/%E3%80%90%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%9B%A0%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E9%A9%85%E9%80%90-%E5%BE%B7%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E3%80%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcnews.com%2Farticle%2F37587%2F%25E7%25A9%2586%25E9%2581%2594%25E5%2581%2589_david_missal-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2581%25AF%25E7%25BD%25B2-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A-37587%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2588%25B0%25E7%25B7%259A%25E3%2580%2591%25E6%259B%25BE%25E5%259B%25A0%25E6%258E%25A1%25E8%25A8%25AA%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E9%25A9%2585%25E9%2580%2590-%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E6%2583%258B%25E6%2583%259C%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%25A4%25B1%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%25EF%25BC%259A%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2582%25BA%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E7%259A%2584%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2599%25BC%25E8%2581%25B2%25E6%2598%25AF%25E6%2588%2591%25E7%259A%2584%25E8%25B2%25AC%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E3%2580%258D&d=auZED%2BZQxHi6416lNwsUjIlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=1b4c0199\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkcnews.com/article/37587/%E7%A9%86%E9%81%94%E5%81%89_david_missal-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2-%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A-37587/%E3%80%90%E5%BE%B7%E5%9C%8B%E6%88%B0%E7%B7%9A%E3%80%91%E6%9B%BE%E5%9B%A0%E6%8E%A1%E8%A8%AA%E7%B6%AD%E6%AC%8A%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E8%A2%AB%E9%A9%85%E9%80%90-%E5%BE%B7%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E6%83%8B%E6%83%9C%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%A4%B1%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%9A%E3%80%8C%E7%82%BA%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC%E8%81%B2%E6%98%AF%E6%88%91%E7%9A%84%E8%B2%AC%E4%BB%BB%E3%80%8D</a>"},{"pid":"c9179e33d80ba8da958dd12694467246f5194b9b","tid":2387823,"uid":219969,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:01:24.000Z","msg":"特別是我作為外國人在國外，為一些不能發聲的人發聲，這個在一定程度上是我的責任吧。<br />\n<br />\n好多謝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好多外國人好落力幫我哋，反而仲上心過好多香港人"},{"pid":"561fa22cdd06c882537979cfc10517e9a34ccfe8","tid":2387823,"uid":146621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89777dc6d93dd9e9c71c84b7a8b0fa8f4cd26335","tid":2387823,"uid":383914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T16:15:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d31103c2